    "final_verdict": "EduBytes shows promising potential but requires significant refinement. Recommendations include: 1) Partner with education experts to validate and improve content quality, 2) Strengthen technical architecture with focus on security and scalability, 3) Develop clear metrics for measuring learning outcomes, 4) Create a more structured content validation process, 5) Establish partnerships with educational institutions for credibility. The project scores above average overall (6.5/10) due to its strong vision and practical application, but needs these improvements to reach its full potential."
